{"tid":215088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【微笑的她】知死期一一安排後事 骨癌少女遺願︰死得美麗","createTime":"2017-04-24T07:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T13:25:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1be50764018c0c9988c213be0879980c27b327","tid":215088,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170423/large/1492940796_8412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170423%2Flarge%2F1492940796_8412.jpg&h=97541e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「如果我死了，我希望死得美麗。」菲律賓20歲女子普雷岡特（Racine Pregunta）不敵癌魔逝世，她控制不了生死，但可以為自己安排身後事，死前數天細意列出喪葬要求，家人全都為她做到了。<br />\n<br />\n普雷岡特患上罕見的骨癌「骨肉瘤」（Osteosarcoma），她上周一病逝。當普雷岡特知道自己不久於人世，便向家人提出遺願，她受喜劇《Die Beautiful》啟發，希望把美麗的最後一刻留在人間、留給家人，她希望在喪禮上穿上露肩白裙、戴上白花頭飾，指定化妝師為她化妝。<br />\n她的姊妹羅蓮(Rolyn)說︰「翌日她要求一些紫色、藍色、薄荷綠的東西。我問她『親愛的，哪是甚麼？』她回答說『你知道的』。」於是家人為她準備了這種顏色的鮮花。<br />\n普雷岡特又希望葬在父親的墓地旁，由於買地問題，結果她的棺木是放在父親棺木上方。家人為普雷岡特完成夢想葬禮，將她打扮得漂漂亮亮，朋友和家人在日落時聚首一堂作最後告別。羅蓮在Facebook悼念她：「今天，遺願已完成，我看到微笑著的你。你永遠在我們心中」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170424/large/1493002962_b250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170424%2Flarge%2F1493002962_b250.jpg&h=0aa74897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170424/56601957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170424%2F56601957&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=1b9db9ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170424%2F56601957&h=2bbf68ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170424/56601957</a>"},{"pid":"214fa19c9bc234da26c72b745f3a901f4790ed43","tid":215088,"uid":42188,"like":0,